	* tp/Texinfo/Common.pm (%def_map),
	* tp/Texinfo/XS/parsetexi/def.c (def_maps):
	Add @deftypeline.

	* tp/Texinfo/ParserNonXS.pm (_gather_def_item, _end_line_def_line),
	* tp/Texinfo/XS/parsetexi/def.c (gather_def_item),
