	* donald_knuth.jpg: New file.

2014-03-03         Arnold D. Robbins     <arnold@skeeve.com>

	* ti.twjr: Rework where initial extraction is done. Set up to
	produce \{ and \}. Works when used with itself to sort the
	index!  Woo hoo!

